which is a very powerful book, had such an effect on me.

76
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:47,000
And also the kind of romances of, was this black guy who used to write all these romances, the foxes of Harrow?

77
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,000
Frank Yurby.

78
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:51,000
Okay, here.

79
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:55,000
