00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:06,000
He said, on the front, Frank was about 14 years old until he left high school.

195
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:11,000
He refused to go because he refused to pay his money and be discriminated against.

196
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:13,000
That's the kind of principle he had.

197
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:18,000
And he was a big burliger, still as tall, big,

198
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:21,000
