00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:46,000
So, look at a driving white folk car.

218
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:50,000
And then they said, we've got a police chief.

219
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:54,000
Now, this is 1959, September, right?

220
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:59,000
So, it predates, and then he a mean cracker.

